Name: pycuGMRES
Version: 1.1.4.6.1
Summary: Fast CUDA C++ GMRES implementation for Toeplitz-like (Toeplitz, Hankel, Circulant) matrices and mixed (combinations of Diagonal ones and Toeplitz-like ones) matrices.
